1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:16,000
This application uses artificial intelligence to process videos by automatically generating transcripts, summer each subtitles, downloadable documents and an AI power chat board that answers questions based on the uploaded video.

2
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,000
I'll run the project.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:32,689
Till the time it loads, I'll explain the text stack.

4
00:00:32,689 --> 00:00:49,689
This project is built using flask for the backend, faster whisper for speech to text transcription, hugging face transformers for AI summarization, movie by an FMP, FFM, PEG for audio extraction,

5
00:00:49,689 --> 00:00:53,689
settings, transformers for chroma DB.

6
00:00:53,689 --> 00:01:00,689
With chroma DB for vector embeddings, OLAMA with LAMA 3.2 for local AI chat board.

7
00:01:00,689 --> 00:01:05,340
I'll open this.

8
00:01:05,340 --> 00:01:16,079
This is the homepage.

9
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:19,079
Here user can upload the video.

10
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:30,079
And also from here, from this drop down, he can select the different languages or to detect is the default.

11
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:32,079
I'll select the video.

12
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:42,049
Now process video.

13
00:01:42,049 --> 00:01:45,049
Now this will take some time.

14
00:01:45,049 --> 00:01:48,049
Within that time, I'll explain further.

15
00:01:48,049 --> 00:01:55,939
Once the video is uploaded, the application performs several operations automatically.

16
00:01:55,939 --> 00:01:59,939
First, the audio is extracted from the video.

17
00:01:59,939 --> 00:02:02,939
Next, faster whisper converts this speech into text.

18
00:02:02,939 --> 00:02:07,939
The transcript is then summarized using an AI summarization model.

19
00:02:07,939 --> 00:02:10,939
Subtitles are generated in SRT format.

20
00:02:10,939 --> 00:02:19,939
The transcript is embedded into chroma DB using sentence transformers, enabling semantic search for the chat board.

21
00:02:19,939 --> 00:02:25,939
Finally, PDF and doc summarizes are generated for download.

22
00:02:25,939 --> 00:02:32,800
Now it's working.

